# BuilderXD

stack: React+TS+Vite | Tailwind v4 | branch=dev
lib: ESM+UMD export (vite lib mode) | peerDeps: react,react-dom

## Bloques (13)
section,column,text,image,button,divider,spacer,social,video,custom_html,countdown,accordion,carousel

## SDK Props
mode,initialTemplate,responsive,onSave,onExport,onTemplateChange,readOnly,theme{primaryColor,darkMode,...},fileManagerProviders[],espIntegrations[]

## API Imperativa (ref)
undo(),redo(),getCode(),setCode(),exportTemplate(format),sendTest(emails[])

## Arch
- Canvas: sandboxed iframe + DOM patch (no srcDoc reload si estructura igual)
- Compiler: Web Worker (compiler.worker.ts) → postMessage {mjml,html}
- History: diff stack (no snapshots)
- i18n: LanguageContext (ES/EN) | Theme: ThemeContext (dark/light, localStorage)
- Modals: FileManager (browse/upload) + ESP (push/pull)

## Pendiente (plan: docs/planes/layout_refinement_plan.md)
- Inspector: reemplazar select/date nativos con widgets custom
- Left panel: grid 2-col, sidebar de tabs
- Bloques faltantes: icon,nav_menu,image_text,product_card,quote
- Canvas: handles de selección, labels de sección, guías

## Branches
main=init only | dev=trabajo activo
